FBIS3-55590 "drsov006_b_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-006 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Official Appointments, Retirements Announced PM1001114194 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI in Russian 10 Jan 94 p 1 PM1001114194 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI Language: Russian Article Type:BFN ["Monitoring" feature: "Cadres"] [Excerpt] The following have been relieved of their posts by edicts of the Russian Federation president: Anatoliy Sliva, who held the post of deputy chief of the Russian Federation President's State Legal Administration and head of department in this administration, in connection with his election as a deputy to the State Duma of the Russian Federation Federal Assembly; Vladimir Sysov, who held the post of chairman of the Russian Federation Committee for Physical Culture, at his own request. Aleksey Glukhov has been appointed Russian Federation Ambassador to the Grand Duchy of Luxembourg by an edict of the Russian Federation president. Chingiz Aytmatov has been relieved of this post in connection with his retirement. [passage omitted]
